58
00:02:35.530 --> 00:02:38.283
Mrs. Logan, that is definitely
not why we'd be here.

59
00:02:38.450 --> 00:02:41.203
You know, actually
my grandfather had the disease

60
00:02:41.370 --> 00:02:43.964
