207
00:09:31.988 --> 00:09:33.956
- OK.
- I just need the dollars.

208
00:09:34.115 --> 00:09:35.833
Oh, right, OK.

209
00:09:35.992 --> 00:09:38.086
Maintenance of <i>daily</i> living
exacts a great toll

210
00:09:38.244 --> 00:09:41.373
