of this disease.

224
00:10:15.490 --> 00:10:16.867
Stave it off!

225
00:10:17.033 --> 00:10:18.831
There's no cure.

226
00:10:18.993 --> 00:10:21.746
And so when I am
in the middle of something

227
00:10:21.913 --> 00:10:26.293
and suddenly my mind
just leaves the premises,

228
00:10:26.459 --> 00:10:30.635
